description: This service has methods for finding Protein Structure Databank (PDB) entries with sequences similar to a KBase protein sequence, specified by either a MD5 id or a feature or coding sequence id. There are two functions, one for searching by MD5, and the other searching by feature ID (FID).
name: protein_structure_service
organization: Office of Scientific and Technical Information (OSTI)
tags: Office of Scientific and Technical Information (OSTI)
